                <h2 id="post-1203">
                    <a href="http://joyridelabs.de/blog/?p=1203" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Nikki&#8217;s Valentines Heart Shirts and Global Game Jam">
                        <span class="blogHeadline">Nikki's Valentines Heart Shirts and Global Game Jam</span>
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <small>Wednesday, February 1st, 2012</small>

                <div>
                    <div class="en"><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://joyridelabs.spreadshirt.de/valentine-girl-A18857760"><img src="http://joyridelabs.de/blog//wp-content/uploads/2012/02/valentine-girl-453.png" alt="Valentines Pixel Neon Heart Female Shirt Design" title="Valentines Pixel Neon Heart Female Shirt Design" width="250" height="280" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1210" /></a><a href="http://joyridelabs.spreadshirt.de/valentine-boy-A18857755"><img src="http://joyridelabs.de/blog//wp-content/uploads/2012/02/valentine-boy-316.png" alt="Valentines Pixel Neon Heart Male Shirt Design" title="Valentines Pixel Neon Heart Male Shirt Design" width="250" height="280" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1211" /></a></p>

<p>We added a neon pixel heart design to our <a href="http://joyridelabs.spreadshirt.de/">shirt store</a>. It is based on one of the first game objects that you will see when playing Episode 1 of the story mode:</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://joyridelabs.de/game/gallery/"><img alt="Nikki and the Robots Neon Heart" src="http://joyridelabs.de/img/screenshot-01.png" title="Nikki and the Robots Neon Heart" class="aligncenter" width="400" height="290" /></a></p>

<p>One of us was at the <a href="http://berlinminijam.blogspot.com/2012/01/ggj-2012-berlin-impressions-and-results.html">Global Game Jam in Berlin</a> as an organizer.</p>

<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://globalgamejam.org/news/2012/01/27/and-ggj-2012-theme"><img src="http://joyridelabs.de/blog//wp-content/uploads/2012/02/ggj2012-topic-theme.png" alt="ggj2012 topic" title="ggj2012 topic" width="256" height="256" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1207" /></a></p>

<p>The theme was a snake biting its own tail and we made a tiny level referencing it. Too late for submission though. ;)</p>

<p><iframe width="540" height="304" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/E6qUI6qPfno" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p style="font-size: small; text-align: center;">video: <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E6qUI6qPfno">Nikki and the Snake - GGJ 2012 Themed Level</a></p>

<p>The video also shows the recently added game over screen menu (no more abrupt returning to the level selection) and a new, simple background for the editor.</p></div>
                </div>
